00:44:48,520 --> 00:44:52,960
I think sometimes just doing it gets you 
over the hump. For example, my friend,  

562
00:44:52,960 --> 00:44:57,440
Ami Vora. She writes an incredible blog. You 
have not read her Substack, you should. But  

563
00:44:57,440 --> 00:45:00,720
she's an incredible writer. She'd write all these 
things internally and I said, "You should publish  

564
00:45:00,720 --> 00:45:05,400
this externally." Now she does that and it's 
really great. And I think part of it was just  

565
00:45:05,400 --> 00:45:11,760
seeing her just put it out there because she 
is one of the wisest career coaches that I have  

566
00:45:11,760 --> 00:45:16,200
and managers that I have ever worked with. And so 
I'm like, "You have so much to say and to share." 

567
00:45:16,200 --> 00:45:20,760
So to see it out there, I feel like for years we 
