568
00:45:20,760 --> 00:45:24,480
But the world was not getting the benefit. So 
in some ways just having accountability. So we  

569
00:45:24,480 --> 00:45:28,360
created a little accountability group to help 
each other write, and it was just a reminder,  

570
00:45:28,360 --> 00:45:33,160
"Hey, did you do it?" And so I think it's 
sometimes what's necessary to get over  

571
00:45:33,160 --> 00:45:37,240
that hump is either having someone forcing you, 
like your manager who you made a commitment to,  

572
00:45:37,240 --> 00:45:41,200
or just having a friend to say, "Hey, 
by the way, where's this month's post?" 

573
00:45:41,200 --> 00:45:46,200
Those things matter because now you got over 
